    <description>Not much is known about the history of this strange Race. It is known that they once lived on a Vulcanian world named Planet-Mora and that they were not always at the top of the food chain or neither the Power. At some point in time they abandoned their home world in search for a Better home, though it's know that was not the Real Reason... Their history is marked by Extreme conflicts around all Universe - Their Capacity to Survive Extreme Temperatures and an Extremely tough Skin composition made them almost Bullet Proof to any Weapon. Until.. until they Invaded a Mysterious System (Turon-96) Home of the Avian-Empire. It was too late until they Realized is was a Big Mistake. Their Dark-Energy weapons slaughtered more then Half of the Vulcanian's. Who survived that Day tells stories of their Mysterious Abilities and the Powerful Lightning Storm's they Casted on their Enemy's. Nowadays there are few Left of this Spices, but all of them Still bring anger about what happened in the past.</description>
